OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1773843068
OL,3,CTwo Cardiff secondary schools remain
OL,4,Cclosed after weapon threats made
OL,6,FThreats making reference to "explosive
OL,7,Fdevices, firearms and knife attacks"
OL,8,Fwere sent to three Cardiff schools, it
OL,9,Fhas been confirmed. South Wales Police
OL,10,Fis continuing to investigate the
OL,11,Fthreats, which saw Llanishen High
OL,12,FSchool and Eastern High School closed
OL,13,Fon Monday and Tuesday, as malicious
OL,14,Fcommunications.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/11
