OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1773843068
OL,3,CTwo Cardiff secondary schools remain
OL,4,Cclosed after weapon threats made
OL,6,FAn update from the force added that
OL,7,Fthe "anonymous online threats", first
OL,8,Fmade to the police's online chat
OL,9,Ffunction on Sunday evening, later
OL,10,Fextended to St Illtyd's High School.
OL,11,FMore information has been released
OL,12,Fabout the nature of the threats, with
OL,13,Fpolice telling local councillors that
OL,14,Fthey made reference to "explosive
OL,15,Fdevices, firearms and knife attacks."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/11
