OL,3,CTwo Cardiff secondary schools remain
OL,4,Cclosed after weapon threats made
OL,6,FFollowing discussion between South
OL,7,FWales Police and Cardiff Council after
OL,8,Fthreats were received, a decision was
OL,9,Fmade to close both Llanishen and
OL,10,FEastern High. Police officers were
OL,11,Fseen at both schools on Monday and
OL,12,Farmed officers were pictured at
OL,13,FEastern High in Trowbridge. Never miss
OL,14,Fa Cardiff story by signing up to our
OL,15,Fdaily newsletter here.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/11
