OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1773843068
OL,3,CTwo Cardiff secondary schools remain
OL,4,Cclosed after weapon threats made
OL,6,F"There is no evidence of capability or
OL,7,Fpreparation to cause harm," it said.
OL,9,FThe schools remained closed on Tuesday
OL,10,Fto allow school staff to meet to
OL,11,Ffinalise plans for additional measures
OL,12,Fdesigned to offer reassurance to
OL,13,Fparents and pupils when the schools
OL,14,Freopen, which is expected to be on
OL,15,FWednesday.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
