SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1773843068
OL,3,CTwo Cardiff secondary schools remain
OL,4,Cclosed after weapon threats made
OL,6,FThe update shared by Cllr Jayne Cowan
OL,7,Fsaid: "South Wales Police continues to
OL,8,Finvestigate anonymous online threats
OL,9,Fmade against Llanishen High School and
OL,10,FEastern High School, later extended to
OL,11,FSt Illtyd's High School. The threats
OL,12,Freference explosive devices, firearms
OL,13,Fand knife attacks.
OL,15,F"The sender remains unidentified, with
OL,16,Fcommunications routed through
OL,17,Fanonymised VPN services.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1773843068
OL,3,CTwo Cardiff secondary schools remain
OL,4,Cclosed after weapon threats made
OL,6,F"The collective partnership assessment
OL,7,Fremains that the threats are
OL,8,Fconditional, disruptive in nature, and
OL,9,Fnot currently assessed as credible
OL,10,Fbased on available intelligence.
OL,12,F"The multiagency position remains
OL,13,Fthat the threats issued to Cardiff
OL,14,Fschools were disruptive rather than
OL,15,Fcredible. Thorough searches,
OL,16,Fintelligence reviews, and
OL,17,Finvestigative activity have confirmed
OL,18,Fthere is no evidence of capability or
OL,19,Fpreparation to cause harm. The police
OL,20,Fcritical incident has been formally
OL,21,Fstood down.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1773843068
OL,3,CTwo Cardiff secondary schools remain
OL,4,Cclosed after weapon threats made
OL,6,F"A proportionate policing and
OL,7,Fpartnership posture continues to
OL,8,Fensure community confidence, support
OL,9,Fsafe school operations, and maintain
OL,10,Fongoing reassurance.
OL,12,F"Partners will remain closely aligned
OL,13,Fthrough Situational Awareness Meeting
OL,14,Fand established communication routes
OL,15,Fbetween parents. A further meeting
OL,16,Fwill be held at 11am on March 17 with
OL,17,Fpartners to discuss recovery stages
OL,18,Fand return to state of normality."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
