PN,46509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1773843068
OL,3,CTwo Cardiff secondary schools remain
OL,4,Cclosed after weapon threats made
OL,6,FThe latest public update from South
OL,7,FWales Police on Tuesday afternoon
OL,8,Fread: "South Wales Police can confirm
OL,9,Fthat information which resulted in two
OL,10,FCardiff schools being closed is now
OL,11,Fbeing investigated as malicious
OL,12,Fcommunications.
OL,14,F"At around 8.30pm on Sunday, March 15
OL,15,Fthe force received a live chat making
OL,16,Fthreats to harm people with weapons at
OL,17,FLlanishen High School and Eastern High
OL,18,FSchool. Further communication was
OL,19,Freceived late last night (Monday,
OL,20,FMarch 16) regarding St Illtyd's High
OL,21,FSchool.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1773843068
OL,3,CTwo Cardiff secondary schools remain
OL,4,Cclosed after weapon threats made
OL,6,F"Extensive enquiries have been
OL,7,Fconducted. Information has been
OL,8,Fassessed and thorough searches have
OL,9,Fbeen conducted at all schools.
OL,10,FSearches were conducted through the
OL,11,Fnight into the early hours of this
OL,12,Fmorning (Tuesday, March 17).
OL,14,F"No evidence has been found of any
OL,15,Fperson attending any of the schools
OL,16,Fposing a threat. We understand that
OL,17,Fevents this week have caused concern
OL,18,Fand disruption for parents and the
OL,19,Fcommunity.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1773843068
OL,3,CTwo Cardiff secondary schools remain
OL,4,Cclosed after weapon threats made
OL,6,F"While the investigation continues to
OL,7,Fdetermine the origin of the malicious
OL,8,Fcommunications, we would ask people to
OL,9,Favoid spreading rumour and
OL,10,Fmisinformation, and to only share
OL,11,Finformation from official sources. We
OL,12,Fthank the schools, parents and the
OL,13,Fwider community for their support and
OL,14,Funderstanding."
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
